>
    <section style="margin-top: 120px;">
        <h1 class="section-title">Dean L. Johnson, M.B.A., J.D. — Attorney & Real Estate Broker</h1>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Attorney-owned buyer's representation with decades of real estate law experience.</p>

        <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 4rem auto;">
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 300px 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: start; background: var(--white); padding: 3rem; border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: 0 4px 30px var(--shadow);">
                <div style="width: 300px; height: 300px; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px var(--shadow);">
